22
00:01:56,961 --> 00:02:01,665
'Ej, kakve cipele? Ako si klovn
bar budi pristojan.

23
00:02:03,934 --> 00:02:07,629
Hajde!

24
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,857
Hajde, idemo!

25
00:02:09,958 --> 00:02:12,225
Uzeli smo tablu!

26
00:02:12,226 --> 00:02:14,772
Držite ih!
- Trči!

27
00:02:14,873 --> 00:02:16,462
Idemo!

28
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:19,607
Stigni nas!

29
00:02:25,762 --> 00:02:29,338
Idemo! Hajde! Nećeš da nas uhvatiš.
- Zaustavite ih!

30
00:02:29,339 --> 00:02:31,447
Mesta!
Sklanjajte se!

31
00:02:34,224 --> 00:02:36,021
Zaustavite ih!

32
00:02:41,886 --> 00:02:43,604
Debilu!

33
00:02:49,668 --> 00:02:50,737
Pogodak!

34
00:02:51,067 --> 00:02:54,073
Prebijte ga! Hajde!
Ne može ništa.

35
00:02:54,074 --> 00:02:55,941
Jače!

36
00:02:55,942 --> 00:02:57,809
Hajde!
Uzmite mu stvari!

37
00:02:57,810 --> 00:03:00,547
Hajde! Hajde! Hajde!

38
00:03:31,047 --> 00:03:35,178
DŽOKER

39
00:04:44,496 --> 00:04:46,068
Da li sam to ja...

40
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:49,241
..ili je izvan nešto ludje?

41
00:04:53,015 --> 00:04:55,847
Stvar je očigledno složena.

42
00:04:56,308 --> 00:04:57,870
Ljudi su razočarani.

43
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:00,482
Bore se, traže posao.

44
00:05:01,213 --> 00:05:03,395
Teška vremena.

45
00:05:05,607 --> 00:05:07,780
A ti?

46
00:05:08,891 --> 00:05:10,803
Vodiš dnevnik?

47
00:05:12,634 --> 00:05:14,196
Da, mem.

48
00:05:15,828 --> 00:05:17,609
Dobro.

49
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:19,932
Kod tebe je?

50
00:05:24,386 --> 00:05:29,361
Arture. Više sam puta molila
da dnevnik nosiš na tretman.

51
00:05:30,202 --> 00:05:31,994
Mogu da pogledam?

52
00:05:43,295 --> 00:05:46,779
Koristim ga kao dnevnik.

53
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:50,122
Ali i kao pregled štoseva.

54
00:05:50,743 --> 00:05:54,486
Smešni fazoni, citati.

55
00:05:55,247 --> 00:05:59,961
Mislim da sam rekao da ću
da se bavim komedijom.

56
00:06:03,185 --> 00:06:04,797
Nisi.

57
00:06:06,518 --> 00:06:08,530
Mislim da jesam.

58
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:20,910
"Nadam se da će moja smrt da
ima više smisla od mog života."

59
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:39,195
Šta čovek oseća kad dodje ovde?

60
00:06:39,351 --> 00:06:42,421
Da li to pomaže?
Da imaš nekom s kim da razgovaraš?

61
00:06:46,198 --> 00:06:50,869
Mislim da mi je bolje dok sam
ležao u bolnici.

62
00:06:51,633 --> 00:06:53,315
Jesi razmišljao...

63
00:06:54,186 --> 00:06:56,058
..zašto si tamo bio?

64
00:07:01,543 --> 00:07:03,955
Ko zna.

65
00:07:10,482 --> 00:07:14,353
Hteo sam da pitam lekara da li
da tražim dopunske lekove.

66
00:07:20,392 --> 00:07:23,400
Arture, koristiš sedam vrsta lekova.

67
00:07:24,236 --> 00:07:27,000
Trebalo bi da imaju
neko desjtvo.

68
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:31,991
Želeo bih da se više
ne osećam loše.

69
00:08:09,029 --> 00:08:11,498
Hoćete da prestanete da
smetate mom detetu?

70
00:08:13,685 --> 00:08:16,318
Ne smetam mu.
- Prestanite!

71
00:08:25,136 --> 00:08:26,437
Nešto vam je smešno?

72
00:08:35,828 --> 00:08:37,499
Izvinite...

73
00:08:39,965 --> 00:08:42,827
OPROSTITE ŠTO SE SMEJEM:
TO JE VRSTA TIKA.

74
00:08:42,851 --> 00:08:45,908
IZNENADNI NEKONTROLISANI NAPAD
SMEHA KOJI NEMA VEZE SA POVODOM.

75
00:08:45,932 --> 00:08:50,270
DEŠAVA SE LJUDIMA SA MENTALNIM
ILI NEUROLOŠKIM POREMEĆAJIMA.

76
00:08:52,594 --> 00:08:54,560
Izvinite.

77
00:10:32,855 --> 00:10:36,000
Dušo, pogledao si u sanduče?

78
00:10:36,468 --> 00:10:38,430
Jesam, mama.

79
00:10:38,550 --> 00:10:40,562
Nema ništa.

80
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:51,443
"Po poslednjim vestima u gradu
je najezda hordi pacova."

81
00:10:51,463 --> 00:10:54,515
" I to ne običnih već
ogromnih pacova."

82
00:10:55,117 --> 00:10:57,579
Sigurno ne dobija moja pisma.

83
00:10:59,281 --> 00:11:01,773
Thomas Vejn, mama.

84
00:11:01,774 --> 00:11:03,164
U poslu je.

85
00:11:03,165 --> 00:11:06,338
Ma hajde.
Radila sam godinama kod njega.

86
00:11:06,658 --> 00:11:08,460
Može bar pismo da mi napiše.

87
00:11:10,192 --> 00:11:12,904
Nemoj da se uzbudjuješ.

88
00:11:14,366 --> 00:11:16,207
Jedi.
- Moraš da jedeš.

89
00:11:16,208 --> 00:11:18,751
Vidi kako si mršav.

90
00:11:23,595 --> 00:11:26,332
Bio bi odličan gradonačelnik.
Svi to kažu.

91
00:11:26,769 --> 00:11:29,020
Da. Ko?

92
00:11:29,021 --> 00:11:30,952
Ko to tako kaže?

93
00:11:30,973 --> 00:11:32,324
Na vestima.

94
00:11:32,875 --> 00:11:35,211
Samo on može da spasi grad.

95
00:11:35,617 --> 00:11:37,139
To nam duguje.

96
00:11:40,082 --> 00:11:42,203
Sedi, počinje.

97
00:11:42,204 --> 00:11:43,625
Marej.

98
00:11:44,433 --> 00:11:49,135
"ENESBI studio Gotam, uživo:"

99
00:11:49,136 --> 00:11:51,278
"Marej Frenklin!"

100
00:11:52,129 --> 00:11:57,881
"Večerašnji gosti Sandra Vinger, komičar
Skip Bajron..." - Sandra Vinger.

101
00:11:57,979 --> 00:12:00,465
"..i omiljena lica medija Jeldon
i Čantel."

102
00:12:00,532 --> 00:12:04,870
"Kao i uvek Mareja prati Elton
Strin i njegov džez orkestar."

103
00:12:05,203 --> 00:12:12,268
"A sada, Marej Frenklin!"

104
00:12:23,306 --> 00:12:24,920
Hvala.

105
00:12:28,851 --> 00:12:30,337
Sjajna je večeras publika.

106
00:12:32,627 --> 00:12:33,628
Hvala. Hvala.

107
00:12:35,932 --> 00:12:39,996
Svi ste sigurno čuli za ogromne
pacove u Gotamu,jelda?

108
00:12:41,357 --> 00:12:45,628
Danas vam gradonačelnik kaže da ima
rešenje, da čujete?

109
00:12:46,467 --> 00:12:48,971
Ogromne mačke!

110
00:12:52,066 --> 00:12:54,979
Mislim ozbiljno.
- Volim te, Marej!

111
00:12:56,841 --> 00:12:58,999
Volim i ja tebe.

112
00:13:00,017 --> 00:13:02,298
Bobi, hajde osvetli.

113
00:13:02,337 --> 00:13:05,349
Ko je to bio? Ti?
Hoćeš da ustaneš, molim te?

114
00:13:05,401 --> 00:13:07,302
Ustani.

115
00:13:07,335 --> 00:13:08,626
Hej.

116
00:13:13,735 --> 00:13:14,736
Kako se zoveš?

117
00:13:16,049 --> 00:13:18,500
Haj, Marej. Artur.

118
00:13:18,570 --> 00:13:19,637
Artur.
- Zovem se Artur.

119
00:13:19,662 --> 00:13:22,765
Dobro, možeš dadodaš još nešto,
Arture, da znamo.

120
00:13:22,819 --> 00:13:25,571
Odakle si?
-Živim ovde u gradu.

121
00:13:25,791 --> 00:13:27,652
S majkom.

122
00:13:28,977 --> 00:13:33,250
Okej, stanite, nije smešno, i ja
sam živeo s majkom dok nisam uspeo.

123
00:13:33,324 --> 00:13:38,596
Samo ona i ja. Otac je otišao da kupi
cigaret i nije se više pojavio.

124
00:13:39,472 --> 00:13:41,450
Znam kakak je to osećaj, Marej.

125
00:13:41,508 --> 00:13:44,071
Celog sam života ja muško u kući.

126
00:13:44,725 --> 00:13:46,893
Brine o svojoj majci.

127
00:13:50,741 --> 00:13:53,452
Toliko žrtvovanje, sigurno
te izuteno voli.

128
00:13:53,499 --> 00:13:54,830
Voli m.

129
00:13:54,854 --> 00:13:58,827
Stalno mi govori da budem nasmejan
i da izgledam srećno.

130
00:13:58,895 --> 00:14:01,631
Kaže da sam rodjen da
donosim sreću i smeh.

131
00:14:09,512 --> 00:14:12,524
Svidja mi se, baš mi se svidja,
sidji ovamo.

132
00:14:12,576 --> 00:14:14,779
Hajde, sidji ovde večeras.

133
00:14:40,865 --> 00:14:42,836
Okej, sjajan nam je šo
večeras.

134
00:14:42,871 --> 00:14:45,607
Budite i dalje tu,
brzo se vraćamo.

135
00:14:46,047 --> 00:14:47,367
Super Arture.

136
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:50,893
Hvala. Divne tvoje reči,
ulepšao si mi dan.

137
00:14:51,045 --> 00:14:52,505
Hvala, Marej.

138
00:14:52,530 --> 00:14:55,484
Vidiš ova svetla, šou, publiku,

139
00:14:55,559 --> 00:14:58,996
sve bih to ostavio za dete koje
ti u sebi nosiš.

140
00:15:40,823 --> 00:15:42,964
Helo, lejdi.
- Kako si, Rendale?

141
00:15:43,001 --> 00:15:44,923
Još jedan dan u ludom gradu.

142
00:15:49,038 --> 00:15:50,919
Dobro si?

143
00:15:52,454 --> 00:15:54,136
Čuo sam za one batine.

144
00:15:55,491 --> 00:15:57,013
Bitange.

145
00:15:58,016 --> 00:16:01,128
Gomila klinaca koju je
trebalo da ostavim na miru.

146
00:16:01,182 --> 00:16:03,994
Ne, ako takav budeš sve
će da ti pokupe.

147
00:16:04,103 --> 00:16:05,994
Čisto ludilo.

148
00:16:06,027 --> 00:16:07,999
Oni su životinje.

149
00:16:12,514 --> 00:16:13,529
Znaš?

150
00:16:19,599 --> 00:16:20,600
Evo.

151
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:22,802
Šta je to?

152
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:24,451
Uzmi.

153
00:16:24,910 --> 00:16:26,588
Za tebe.

154
00:16:30,855 --> 00:16:33,090
Moraš da sebe zaštitiš.

155
00:16:33,288 --> 00:16:35,580
Inače si nadrljao.

156
00:16:36,598 --> 00:16:38,930
Pištolj?

157
00:16:39,222 --> 00:16:41,944
Ne bi smeo to da nosim.

158
00:16:44,116 --> 00:16:45,648
Nema problema.

159
00:16:45,728 --> 00:16:47,097
Neće niko da zna.

160
00:16:47,199 --> 00:16:49,352
Platićeš mi drugi put.

161
00:16:49,585 --> 00:16:51,877
Dobar si ti momak.

162
00:16:53,168 --> 00:16:56,448
Arture, Zove te Hojt u kancelariju.

163
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:59,532
Geri, znaš šta sam se
uvek pitao?

164
00:16:59,581 --> 00:17:01,012
Ne znam.

165
00:17:01,037 --> 00:17:05,108
Da li to zovete mini golf ili
vam je to samo golf?

166
00:17:28,003 --> 00:17:29,733
Helo, Hojte.

167
00:17:29,734 --> 00:17:32,396
Kaže Geri da si me tražio.

168
00:17:32,553 --> 00:17:35,176
Kako ide karijera?
Postao si faca?

169
00:17:35,474 --> 00:17:38,828
Još radim na tome.

170
00:17:38,946 --> 00:17:41,518
Ne sedaj.
Brzo ćemo. Vidi...

171
00:17:41,919 --> 00:17:46,757
Dopadaš mi se, Arture, mnogi misle
da si čudak, ali meni se dpadaš.

172
00:17:47,269 --> 00:17:48,620
Ne znam zašto.

173
00:17:48,983 --> 00:17:50,993
Ali ima jedna žalba.

174
00:17:51,493 --> 00:17:53,922
Počinjem da se brinem.
Kenis Mjuzik.

175
00:17:53,991 --> 00:17:55,833
Čovek kaže da si se izgubio.

176
00:17:56,292 --> 00:17:57,914
Nisi vratio natpis.

177
00:17:58,612 --> 00:18:00,794
Jer su me napali.

178
00:18:00,832 --> 00:18:02,023
Nisi me čuo?

179
00:18:02,885 --> 00:18:05,541
Zbog natpisa? Gluposti.

180
00:18:05,595 --> 00:18:07,216
Nema logike.

181
00:18:07,245 --> 00:18:09,046
Vrati im to.

182
00:18:09,077 --> 00:18:11,621
Treba im, Arture.

183
00:18:11,622 --> 00:18:13,764
Šta će meni natpis?

184
00:18:13,892 --> 00:18:16,000
Odakle ja to znam?

185
00:18:17,353 --> 00:18:21,958
Ako im ne vratiš moraću
da ti skinem od plate.

186
00:18:23,023 --> 00:18:24,987
Razumeš?

187
00:18:25,629 --> 00:18:28,770
Slušaj, pokušavam da ti pomognem.

188
00:18:29,001 --> 00:18:30,970
Okej, još ću nešto da ti kažem...

189
00:18:30,971 --> 00:18:33,350
Ima ljudi kojima
nije baš prijatno...

190
00:19:28,233 --> 00:19:30,925
Sačekajte, sačekajte!

191
00:19:34,209 --> 00:19:36,000
Hvala.

192
00:19:57,265 --> 00:20:00,102
Ova je zgrada očajna.

193
00:20:01,755 --> 00:20:04,616
Ova je zgrada očajna, mama?

194
00:20:04,665 --> 00:20:07,097
Jeste, dušo.

195
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:10,013
Očajna je, mama.

196
00:20:12,464 --> 00:20:13,465
A, mama?

197
00:20:20,017 --> 00:20:22,930
Očajna je ova zgrada?

198
00:20:56,276 --> 00:21:00,229
Spusti glavu.
- Možda ga je poštar bacio.

199
00:21:00,297 --> 00:21:03,000
Mama, što ti je to
pismo toliko bitno?

200
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:07,130
Šta misliš da će on da uradi?
- Pomoćiće nam.

201
00:21:08,140 --> 00:21:13,212
Radila si tamo pre trideset godina,
što bi nom pomagao?

202
00:21:13,918 --> 00:21:16,120
Zato što je Tomas Vejn
dobar čovek.

203
00:21:17,429 --> 00:21:20,248
Da zna kako živimo.

204
00:21:20,249 --> 00:21:23,000
Zgrozio bi se da može da vidi
ovo mesto.

205
00:21:24,759 --> 00:21:27,061
Nemam drugo objašnjenje.

206
00:21:30,022 --> 00:21:31,556
Ne sekiraj se oko Vejna.

207
00:21:32,811 --> 00:21:33,952
Ni oko mene.

208
00:21:34,225 --> 00:21:38,329
Kažu mi svi da sam spreman da
nastupam u velikom klubu.

209
00:21:39,346 --> 00:21:41,959
Dušo, misliš li da si
to u stanju?

210
00:21:42,481 --> 00:21:44,123
Kako misliš?

211
00:21:45,474 --> 00:21:48,997
Ne misliš li da treba da budeš
duhovit da bi bio komičar?

212
00:22:51,315 --> 00:22:54,558
Haj, kako se zoveš?
Artur.

213
00:22:55,621 --> 00:22:59,195
Haj, Arture, dobar si plesač.

214
00:22:59,652 --> 00:23:02,208
Znam?

215
00:23:09,190 --> 00:23:11,531
Dušo, jesi dobro?

216
00:23:11,572 --> 00:23:14,644
Mama, šta?
- Šta se tamo dešava?

217
00:23:14,797 --> 00:23:17,539
Gledam ratni film.

218
00:23:17,588 --> 00:23:20,421
Utišaj!

219
00:23:25,071 --> 00:23:27,003
Izvini.

220
00:24:48,064 --> 00:24:51,001
Drago mi je što ovde vidim
parove.

221
00:24:51,321 --> 00:24:53,744
Imam ženu, volimo da se igramo.

222
00:24:54,263 --> 00:24:56,684
Da, da, baš seksi.

223
00:24:56,727 --> 00:25:02,793
Omiljena mi je igra
profesora i studentkinje.

224
00:25:06,509 --> 00:25:08,230
Ide ovako:

225
00:25:08,260 --> 00:25:11,053
Ja sam profesor na fakultetu.

226
00:25:12,281 --> 00:25:16,545
Moja supruga je na završnoj godini
upoznavanja zapadne kulture.

227
00:25:18,236 --> 00:25:21,618
