hladni, mračni svet.

378
00:43:00,084 --> 00:43:02,746
Okej.

379
00:43:02,792 --> 00:43:06,385
Molim vas da pozdravite
Artura Fleka!

380
00:43:30,688 --> 00:43:32,891
Helo...

381
00:43:57,473 --> 00:44:01,162
Mrzeo sam školu kao dete.

382
00:44:15,779 --> 00:44:19,763
Mrzeo sam školu...
kao dete.

383
00:44:21,510 --> 00:44:24,105
Majka mi je govorila,

384
00:44:24,106 --> 00:44:27,860
uživaj, jednog ćeš dana da
zaradjuješ za život.

385
00:44:29,656 --> 00:44:30,764
Ne, mama.

386
00:44:30,784 --> 00:44:33,496
Ja ću da budem komičar.

387
00:44:44,837 --> 00:44:45,843
Evo nešto.

388
00:44:47,102 --> 00:44:51,193
Razmišljao sam pre neki dan,

389
00:44:51,673 --> 00:44:53,934
zašto svi...

390
00:45:20,642 --> 00:45:23,627
"KLOVN UBICA JOŠ NA SLOBODI"

391
