Veruješ u to?

392
00:45:34,983 --> 00:45:36,919
"KLOVN OSVETNIK?"

393
00:45:36,939 --> 00:45:37,940
ko ih jebe!

394
00:45:38,721 --> 00:45:41,068
Po meni je čova koji je
to uradio junak.

395
00:45:43,102 --> 00:45:45,438
Tri debila manje u Gotamu.

396
00:45:45,741 --> 00:45:47,933
Ostalo ih je još milion.

397
00:46:26,550 --> 00:46:29,423
"Sutra uveče nastupaju Dijana Hadson,"

398
00:46:29,553 --> 00:46:33,386
"Grant Gordon, i ekspert za životinje
Hju Litl."

399
00:46:33,452 --> 00:46:35,173
"Hvala vam što ste gledali."

400
