433
00:52:55,004 --> 00:52:56,005
Brus.

434
00:52:57,463 --> 00:52:59,158
Ja sam Artur.

435
00:53:24,476 --> 00:53:25,846
Bruse!

436
00:53:25,847 --> 00:53:28,776
